After a long while of flying, Hellpeon arrives at the Oteybis. Well 
in its vicinity. He circles over the portion of the ship in which 
Demonite and Diablo landed on and shortly afterwards hovers down in 
front of their ships. He stands there, his arms folded over his chest 
as he waits for someone to acknowledge him.
